Interface UnauthenticatedJob<P extends java.io.Serializable,R extends java.io.Serializable>

  • Type Parameters:
    P - job parameter type
    R - job return value type
    All Superinterfaces:
    Job<P,R>

    public interface UnauthenticatedJob<P extends java.io.Serializable,R extends java.io.Serializable>
extends Job<P,R>
    Marker interface which indicates that the job doesn't need to be authenticated before execution by ClusterExecutor. Note, PRThread won't be created for this job.
